The '''Flames of Umate''' were a religious cult on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. They were centered on [[Umate/Legends|Umate]], the highest peak of the [[Manarai Mountains]] and the only outcropping of natural [[Stone/Legends|stone]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] surface. Their monks meditated while touching the rock in an effort to contact Coruscant's 'inner spirit'. They also patrolled the peak, preventing tourists from chipping off souvenirs from the stone.

